    "description": "I don't know why, but the baby pufferfish is always bouncing on the floor.<br />\r\nThere's never been a pause!<br />\r\nDelicate manipulation will be needed to safely take the baby pufferfish to its destination.<br />\r\nHelp baby pufferfish reach their destination safely through proper response speed and control.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt re-interpreted the classic game BouncingBall and contains several unique stages.<br />\r\nYou can play it lightly, but you can also build up your skills through many attempts if you want.<br />\r\nChallenge yourself to speedrun!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✸ 50 different stage levels.<br />\r\n✸ Experience simple manipulation and a variety of gimmicks.<br />\r\n✸ Solve the puzzle using special tiles in many ways.<br />\r\n✸ Collect coins from every stage!<br />\r\n✸ Challenge Clear Record with the shortest time!",
